<dl id="jn1012h"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="jn1" href="#jn1012">JN1: </a>  <a href="../../ff/unbs/jn1all.htm#jn1012h"> (NLI.2A) 12(h)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> It is in beings that are always the same and are not susceptible / of change that we must seek for (the) truth.</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources"><mark>On ne doit chercher &agrave; trouver la v&eacute;rit&eacute; que dans les choses qui sont &eacute;ternellement les m&ecirc;mes, et qui ne subissent jamais le moindre changement</mark>. <small> Aristotle, <a name="MABS" href="/udra/udex.htm#mabs"><cite title="source">M&eacute;taphysique d'Aristote</cite></a> (1879), III, 101</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
